(ReAct, Skeleton-of-Thought, Extended-Thinking, Step-Back,
Constitutional-Self-Critique, Chain-of-Verification, Inline-WHY) to
the corresponding Sophia SDD phase. The rule content and inline-why
explanations are original adaptations for the sophia-orchestator
domain and are not verbatim copies of Cortex-IA source.
